    <h2>Know This</h2>

    <ul>
      <li>Your login is maintained using a token file in your ~/.weblog/ folder, keep it safe.</li>
      <li>SSL is provided by startssl, in the free tier.</li>
      <li>IPs are logged because curl sends them and the web server stores them by default.</li>
      <li>There is no password recovery system, an account lost is lost forever</li>
      <li>The site does not use cookies or third party tracking, but Google Fonts might be</li>
    </ul>

